  lines:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "What is this thing\u2026? But I suppose you were right, there is rainwater
      here."
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: "Of course I was. And this \u201Cthing\u201D here is a Dowsing Stone."
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: A what?
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: 'A Dowsing Stone. It was used by some people to feel the flow of underground
      water, and predict where it would pop up. '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: 'How do you know that? '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: "Well this venerable stone and I\u2026Well, we are basically cousins, you
      could say. Though this one has long since fallen asleep\u2026"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "So if we use this thing\u2026Somehow\u2026we can find more water? "
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: 'Of course we can. '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "But that would mean\u2026Facing more eyes\u2026Right\u2026?"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: Most certainly.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "I\u2019m not ready for this\u2026"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: How about we just try it, and take a decision afterwards?
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "...I guess we could do that\u2026But how do we use it?"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: Well, you cannot feel the flow yourself, but I might be able to help with
      that. You will have to place me atop the stone in just the right way.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: If you do so, I will be able to feel what the dowsing stone feels.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: In just the right way?
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: Yes. In the right spot, and in the right inclination. You will pick it
      up quickly, do not worry.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7b9571e32814fbb42b8e4653389490d6, type: 2}
    text: "I\u2019m not as confident as you are, but I can give it a try\u2026"
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8096678c4d8dc234d949df06177fdd34, type: 2}
    text: Let us go ahead then. The right spot. And the right inclination. Keep those
      two things in mind and you will do great.
  automatic: 0
